        "created_at": "2024-05-14T07:36:05.450Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Am I right: this is not the 2nd wine of Ch.Lafleur ( which is Pensees de L.) but a different (new) property in Fronsac?<br>\nGrand Village is another property of this family?</p>\n<p>I ve tasted Lafleur (great), Pensees (usually fine), Grand Village ( good, but simple), but never Perrieres. 1st vintage 2018?</p>",
