        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/3bc359/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2024-05-14T08:03:05.968Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It is a different property in Fronsac yes. The wine was called \u201cActe 1\u201d for the first release from the 2009 vintage. Then you had Acte 2/3 etc. till 2017 and the Acte 9.</p>\n<p>In 2018 they changed the label and called it Les Perri\u00e8res, a fantastic name.</p>\n<p>Surprisingly or not, the price evolved dramatically as well (between *2 and *3).</p>",
